    <div class="definition-box">
      <h3>FERPA (Family Educational Rights and Privacy Act)</h3>
      <p>Protects the privacy of student education records in the US. Schools must have written consent before releasing information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="definition-box">
      <h3>COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act)</h3>
      <p>Regulates online collection of personal info from children under 13. Websites must get parental consent.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="definition-box">
      <h3>GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation)</h3>
      <p>A European Union regulation to protect personal data. Emphasizes consent, transparency, and the right to be forgotten.</p>
    </div>
